<HEADLINE>
FT  25 SEP 93 / World News in Brief: Prost to retire
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
French grand prix driver Alain Prost, 38, who will be world champion for the
fourth time if he wins in Portugal tomorrow, is to retire at the end of the
season.
